<h2 id="httpwwwroyalmailcomfind-a-postcode"><a href="http://www.royalmail.com/find-a-postcode">http://www.royalmail.com/find-a-postcode</a></h2>

<p>Royal Mail postcode finder which narrows results as you type, providing an immediate total of any matches including whole of address and partial words.
The api returns 7 matching results whilst a partial postcode is provided.</p>

<p>http://api.postcodefinder.royalmail.com/CapturePlus/Interactive/Find/v2.10/json3ex.ws?Key=BH89-YF22-ZU91-EE62&amp;Country=GBR&amp;SearchTerm=se109aq</p>

